WEBVTT

00:01:29.132 --> 00:01:30.886
"Don't you want a family?"

00:01:32.463 --> 00:01:34.639
"Don't you want to leave anything behind?"

00:01:36.106 --> 00:01:41.977
And the primary buzzword
when discussing childlessness,

00:01:42.001 --> 00:01:43.443
"That's selfish."

00:01:47.252 --> 00:01:50.585
There are countless reasons
a woman may have

00:01:50.609 --> 00:01:53.705
for choosing to abstain from motherhood,

00:01:53.729 --> 00:01:56.594
the majority of them
not self-prioritizing.

00:01:58.094 --> 00:02:02.396
But it is still socially acceptable
to publicly vilify women as such,